  <div class="wrapper">
   <section class="intro">
    <h1>
     A Celebration of 100 Years Begins with One Unforgettable Day.
    </h1>
    <p>
     UCLA will begin its Centennial Celebration on Saturday, May 18, 2019, with a day of events happening all over campus. Join us as we celebrate all that UCLA has achieved in 100 short years, while looking ahead to another century of illumination and impact. The day is open to the entire UCLA community: alumni, students, staff, faculty, families, friends and fans.
    </p>
   </section>
   <section class="events">
    <div>
     <img alt="UCLA Alumni Day" src="img/ucla_alumni_day.png"/>
     <h2>
      Alumni Day 2019
     </h2>
     <p>
      Alumni Day returns to campus amid the joyful celebration of 100 years of Bruin achievement. Campus will be bustling with excitement as we honor the history and legacy of our centennial and lean into a limitless future. There will be timely speakers, engaging discussions, enlightening tours and yet-to-be-imagined surprises. You won’t want to miss this. Save the date and make plans now. We’ll see you there.
     </p>
     <a class="btn gtm-cta-link-outbound" href="https://alumniday.ucla.edu" target="_blank">
      Go to alumniday.ucla.edu
     </a>
    </div>
    <div>
     <img alt="TEDxUCLA" src="img/tedx_ucla.jpg"/>
     <h2>
      TEDxUCLA 2019
     </h2>
     <p>
      TEDxUCLA proudly presents TIME, the theme of our 2019 conference. Awe-inspiring talks and adventures are crafted to engage your mind and challenge your paradigms as we explore the idea of time. Save the date and spend some of your time with us on Saturday May 18 at UCLA’s historic Royce Hall.
     </p>
     <a class="btn gtm-cta-link-outbound" href="https://tedx.ucla.edu" target="_blank">
      Go to tedx.ucla.edu
     </a>
    </div>
    <div>
     <img alt="Lighting the Way" src="img/centennial100_opening.jpg"/>
     <h2>
      Centennial 100 Opening Event
     </h2>
     <p>
      Join the Bruin family in Dickson Plaza for a special light and sound projection show inspired by 100 years of innovation, optimism, and world-changing achievements that are “Lighting the Way.”
     </p>
     <p class="bold-italic">
      Opening Event sign-up coming soon.
     </p>
    </div>
